        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 11. Cossura keablein. sp. Paratype, W.42862, SEM.(A) general view; thorax and beginning of abdomen; anterior end:posterolateral view, abdomen: ventral view; (B) anterior end, lateral view (arrow indicates lateral organ); (C) notopodia of chaetiger 3; (D) neuropodia of chaetiger 4; (E) parapodia of chaetigers 18–20; (F) abdominal parapodia. Scale bars: A, B = 100 μm, C–F = 20 μm." ;
